{"tid":625071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【華明邨毒狗案】 一星期十狗中毒亡","createTime":"2018-04-11T06:41:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T07:22:12.000Z","uid":181569,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4d11364c8330991be3e170fd3916c80bcf682b58","tid":625071,"uid":181569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:41:00.000Z","msg":"由4月開始至昨日<br />\n華明邨已經死左十隻狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢地毒發果陣都係四腳伸直<br />\n張開雙眼但雙目無神  不斷抽筋<br />\n半小時後就身亡<br />\n<br />\n其中一隻遇害狗仔: 松鼠狗 安力史<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180406/large/1522945907_113e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180406%2Flarge%2F1522945907_113e.jpg&h=d2d46358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個咁高危既時間 大家盡量唔好帶狗狗落街<br />\n我都明好多狗仔落慣街<br />\n突然唔落係唔得<br />\n<br />\n但系記住落之前<br />\n要幫狗仔戴口罩<br />\n以免狗仔食到或者索到毒藥<br />\n盡量拖住繩行<br />\n番到屋企之後 一定要洗乾淨手手腳腳<br />\n<br />\n希望大家見到呢個消息<br />\n盡快通知有養狗既人"},{"pid":"15d15495daa9454d73da76c4dd51464a772d796f","tid":625071,"uid":181569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"蘋果報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180410/58056656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58056656&d=kQgFSJP9XBHiOkgzvsGqHnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=06d06338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180410%2F58056656&h=eaf720a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180410/58056656</a>"},{"pid":"11f44703e92ee5a5f25854c9cdcfb4524643fa3f","tid":625071,"uid":147586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:54:28.000Z","msg":"可憐"},{"pid":"6c160910a22ced890ed30e18ffa2bad8b63458c7","tid":625071,"uid":74908,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"系你老母"},{"pid":"c91507d08b321bfe4fbc2bcbd7766c9857514890","tid":625071,"uid":61675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"系你老母<br />\n和興體育館出面成條都係狗屎路<br />\n<br />\n不過要死既應該係d 主人唔係d 寵物"},{"pid":"462219693fea7a375264ecdf21dfc0cd897d0ce5","tid":625071,"uid":181569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c91507d08b321bfe4fbc2bcbd7766c9857514890","tid":625071,"uid":61675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:15:28.000Z","msg":"系你老母<br />\n和興體育館出面成條都係狗屎路<br />\n<br />\n不過要死既應該係d 主人唔係d 寵物"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T07:22:12.000Z","msg":"最衰都系啲不負責任既狗主<br />\n同埋落毒殺狗既凶手<br />\n先會引致呢件事發生<br />\n狗仔佢地好無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}